{"tid":870630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台鐵普悠馬號列車於宜蘭出軌翻側","createTime":"2018-10-21T09:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T18:39:12.000Z","uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"08cf10bb87481c675f0a87000b9ead3b0d2cd873","tid":870630,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T09:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/174050_95a445da7b816bf62a510d99e4ac10d3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F174050_95a445da7b816bf62a510d99e4ac10d3.png&h=2d99300c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台鐵發生嚴重意外。台灣宜蘭蘇澳新馬車站外，普悠瑪列車今日下午4時50分發生翻覆意外，目前相關單位已趕往現場搶救，詳細受傷狀況仍待進一步了解。台鐵起成立局本部一級應變小組王處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181021&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58819360\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181021%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58819360&d=yQ1H4pfcVVV0M7YmnUE%2B49U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=de693548\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181021%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58819360&h=e44bc0a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181021&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58819360</a>"},{"pid":"0ca63fe4b5cda973812b6a70d404ac5fa3ad57a7","tid":870630,"uid":36238,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T09:42:06.000Z","msg":"中國台灣"},{"pid":"d1964e4924380d713a1747d09a3349a1c79c875c","tid":870630,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T09:42:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lKcSCLg25Fw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlKcSCLg25Fw&d=yQ1H4pfcVVV0M7YmnUE%2B49U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=193b7f9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lKcSCLg25Fw</a>"},{"pid":"daca1652122bfb62b2f95bd1a76feeea47d3adbf","tid":870630,"uid":179467,"like":3,"di