_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/36238</a><br />\n起底望下條假膠先覆啦下次.."},{"pid":"1dc4f5e3d5218bd2c908b2e5b9d1a5ab3ce133e4","tid":870630,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T10:44:35.000Z","msg":"台鐵好似隔一段時間就會出現出軌的意外<br />\n有冇人知點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"945764bef1e2509c051cdf103f19de8904a5e5ba","tid":870630,"uid":190333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dc4f5e3d5218bd2c908b2e5b9d1a5ab3ce133e4","tid":870630,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T10:44:35.000Z","msg":"台鐵好似隔一段時間就會出現出軌的意外<br />\n有冇人知點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T10:47:22.000Z","msg":"對上一次應該係泰魯閣號平交道炒車"},{"pid":"fc5a80932941a06cab693be0a5ea4b27246ccb3f","tid":870630,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"945764bef1e2509c051cdf103f19de8904a5e5ba","tid":870630,"uid":190333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dc4f5e3d5218bd2c908b2e5b9d1a5ab3ce133e4","tid":870630,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T10:44:35.000Z","msg":"台鐵好似隔一段時間就會出現出軌的意外<br />\n有冇人知點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T10:47:22.000Z","msg":"對上一次應該係泰魯閣號平交道炒車"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T10:49:19.000Z","msg":"唔係，呢兩年都有出軌<br />\n<br />\n作為台鐵最快的車型，普悠瑪由日本車輛公司生產，來往台北至台東路段，最高時速為每小時160公里。去年10月24日，一列台東開往新北樹林的普悠瑪號列車，下午4時20分行經花蓮三民站時，第2至6車發生出軌事故，幸好當時車速不快，車上300名乘客平安無事，但要下車步行至車站。<br />\n<br />\n而在2016年，台鐵307次自強號新左營站開往花蓮列車，下午駛經花蓮瑞穗鄉時，列車最後三節車廂突然出現翻側及出軌，軌道出現明顯彎曲。意外釀成兩名大陸客受傷，3,000多名乘客受影響，及至少25班列車誤點。這是台灣當時一個月內發生的第二宗火車事故，當時有指或因天氣太熱致路軌變形，值得留意的是，當年同月4日曾發生莒光號出軌事故，位置相距約50公里<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181021/58819450\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181021%2F58819450&d=yQ1H4pfcVVV0M7YmnUE%2B49U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=b4c6e764\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181021%2F58819450&h=6a0af822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181021/58819450</a>"}]}